title: The Faces Of The Cigar Industry
itunes:title: The Faces Of The Cigar Industry
description: The Face of the Cigar Industry. Who is it, who are the faces of the cigar industry, and the Cigar Brands... and while we're at it... who is the face of The Cigar Authority. You might be surprised! We light up La Galera Box Pressed and the all new Fratello Firecracker. We got all that and a couple of big announcements!
